Wow.

23
00:01:49.509 --> 00:01:50.610
Hi. Millie!

24
00:01:50.611 --> 00:01:53.008
Hi. Mrs. Winchester!

25
00:01:53.009 --> 00:01:54.075
So nice to meet you.

26
00:01:54.076 --> 00:01:55.345
